ygData.subject: Clerics in Bristlebane
ygData.msgSnippet: Greetings everyone, This is your friendly neighborhood Dwarfen Cleric, Vrachit. Just wanted to say hello and also ask if others are finding it as hard as I am
ygData.messageBody:
Greetings everyone,

This is your friendly neighborhood Dwarfen Cleric, Vrachit. Just wanted
to say hello and also ask if others are finding it as hard as I am from
level 6 and up. I am 6 now and having hard time finding good things to
kill or parties to kill them will. I am often found in freeport but
spend most of my time in Butcherblock, as it is easier to fetch my
corpse (which I seem to be doing a lot of lately).

Any advice you have for this struggling healer would be most
appreciated.
